  "summary": "Mattermost doesn't limit the size of the request body on the start meeting API endpoint",
  "details": "Mattermost versions 11.5.x \u003c= 11.5.1, 10.11.x \u003c= 10.11.13, 11.4.x \u003c= 11.4.3 fail to limit the size of the request body on the start meeting API endpoint, which allows an authenticated attacker to cause resource exhaustion or denial of service via a crafted oversized HTTP POST request to {{/api/v1/meetings}}.. Mattermost Advisory ID: MMSA-2026-00608",
